---
Name: AI Video Content Creator
Description: Generate an AI-powered video by creating a transcript, converting it to speech, generating images, and merging everything into a video.
Param: user_prompt: The input text to generate the transcript from.
Param: openai_api_key: The OpenAI API key to be used in the script.

#!/bin/sh
npm install
USER_PROMPT="$user_prompt" OPENAI_API_KEY="$openai_api_key" node script.js

